          "en": "she has tried a new car"
        },
        {
          "no": "læreren prøvde elevene i grammatikk",
          "en": "the teacher tested the students in grammar"
        },
        {
          "no": "saken vil bli prøvd for retten",
          "en": "the case will be tried in court"
        }
